# AI Chaos Scout — OPTIONAL environment variables.
#
# The core path (Tier-2 sourcing + all 3 report artifacts) needs NONE of these.
# Copy to `.env` only if you want an optional layer. Never commit `.env`.

# --- Gemini image stretch (off by default) --------------------------------
# If set, Stage 3 generates one concept visual per track's top rec (design-language
# styled), embedded in the standalone HTML (data-URI) and the .eml (cid). If unset,
# it is skipped silently and the layout does not depend on it.
# GEMINI_API_KEY=

# --- Tier-1 adapters (UNTESTED SCAFFOLDS, enabled: false) ------------------
# Present only so the scaffolds have documented env contracts. Setting these does
# NOT make the adapters production-ready — they are untested by design.
# X_BEARER_TOKEN=
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=
# GREPTILE_API_KEY=
# GITHUB_TOKEN=
# MSGRAPH_TENANT_ID=
# MSGRAPH_CLIENT_ID=
# MSGRAPH_CLIENT_SECRET=
# MSGRAPH_DRIVE_ID=

# NOTE: Composio (the sanctioned delivery layer) uses URL-based MCP OAuth, NOT an
# API key in this repo — see .cursor/mcp.json and docs/composio.md.
